OL,3,CSurgeries postponed in Guernsey as
OL,4,Chospital exceeds capacity limit
OL,6,F14 patients in Guernsey have had their
OL,7,Fsurgeries postponed this week due to
OL,8,Fcapacity at the Princess Elizabeth
OL,9,FHospital exceeding its limit.
OL,11,FIslanders are warned to expect further
OL,12,Fcancellations until the issue has been
OL,13,Fresolved with cancer and emergency
OL,14,Fsurgeries the priority.
OL,16,FThe States of Guernsey says: "The
OL,17,FPrincess Elizabeth Hospital is
OL,18,Fcurrently at over capacity so some
OL,19,Felective surgeries have unfortunately,
OL,20,Fbut unavoidably, had to be postponed
OL,21,Fto ensure safe practice."
