OL,3,CSurgeries postponed in Guernsey as
OL,4,Chospital exceeds capacity limit
OL,6,FFurther beds have been added to
OL,7,Fpatient wards to ensure staff are
OL,8,Ffocused on caring for the additional
OL,9,Fadmissions.
OL,11,FThe Health and Social Care department
OL,12,Fsays it recognises it is always
OL,13,Fdisappointing when elective surgery
OL,14,Fmust be postponed and apologises for
OL,15,Fthe impact this has on individuals and
OL,16,Ftheir families.
OL,18,FIt adds: "There is no single factor
OL,19,Fimpacting acute care and it is a
OL,20,Fseasonal issue with demand
OL,21,Foutstripping available capacity.
