OL,3,CSurgeries postponed in Guernsey as
OL,4,Chospital exceeds capacity limit
OL,6,F"Teams from both the hospital and
OL,7,Fcommunity have worked tirelessly to
OL,8,Fminimise the number of postponed
OL,9,Felective surgeries and safe discharges
OL,10,Fout of the hospital.
OL,12,F"We have also increased capacity
OL,13,Fwithin the Day Patient Unit to ensure
OL,14,Fsome surgeries can still take place
OL,15,Fand to utilise theatre capacity."
OL,17,FThe hospital reassures patients that
OL,18,Fthe situation is being monitored and
OL,19,Fpostponed elective cases will be
OL,20,Frearranged as soon as possible.
